cu.explanation_en: Setting Num_Threads_PUSCH to an invalid value will cause thread initialization errors and system startup failure.

du.explanation_en: Setting Num_Threads_PUSCH to an invalid value will cause thread initialization errors and system startup failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 Num_Threads_PUSCH 設定為無效值會導致線程初始化錯誤和系統啟動失敗。
